[:zh_CN]
操作数是多态类类型的泛左值的 typeid 表达式（[#expr.typeid]）；

[item]
[:en]
a [~new-expression] ([#expr.new]);
[:zh_CN]
[~new-表达式]（[#expr.new]）；

[item]
[:en]
a [~delete-expression] ([#expr.delete]);
[:zh_CN]
[~delete-表达式]（[#expr.delete]）；

[item]
[:en]
a relational ([#expr.rel]) or equality ([#expr.eq]) operator where the result is
